thread.title: Donna

author: Donna
title: Donna
text: The plaque and engraving were good. However the lucite cover for the scorecard was difficult to remove. One screw holding the cover onto the plaque could not be removed causing me to crack the corner of the cover and placing the scorecard in without centering it. I seriously debated demanding a replacement but will consider another plaque company if I ever have another hole in one.
